%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

Overview:
This directory contains code that is specific to the host-model. This is where you:
   *) Set working types used COSP.
   *) Set physical and mathematical constants used in COSP.
   *) Handle error reporting.

Contents:
cosp_constants.f90:     Physical and mathematical constants used within COSP
cosp_kinds.f90:         Type(s) used within COSP.
cosp_errorHandling.f90: Controls error reporting.
